an 2 doses should be given daily.[L6793,L6796,L6799,L6805,L6808,L6811] Medication overuse headaches may occur in patients who use sumatriptan frequently.[L6793,L6796,L6799,L6805,L6808,L6811]', 'DrugBank', 0, 0, 0);
